        <h4>Crown of Courage</h4>
        <p>Book 1 of the Three Kingdoms Trilogy. Callan should be crowned by now, but the Crown of Courage has been stolen, and without it, he cannot be considered a legitimate ruler of Riax. Talien has always run from responsibility, but the chance to prove he was the best was too good to pass up and oops... now he’s a knight. Camelyn isn’t the most open, but that’s to be expected when, as the first female knight in history, the world seems against her. Together, the three must retrieve the crown, before the kingdom falls.</p>
