        <p>Enovia, a world of floating islands, has existed for centuries, governed by the Caleum Empire and the Fyra Alliance. When the capitol city of Caleum drifts beyond the atmosphere and disappears, the world is thrown into chaos. Milus - a captain in the military, his daughter Amara, and Lilja - a lower-islander, may be the key to the survival of the islands.</p>
